data.description: Super clean unit on pond with full caged lanai. Plantation shutters in front of unit with nice shades for the back. Crown moulding and higher baseboards. Freshly painted, new HVAC (2021) and water heater (2022). Washer and dryer just two years old. Open floor plan and nice layout with arched entryways. Two good sized bedrooms. Den at front foyer has closet and could be used as third bedroom. Great location, friendly, active neighborhood. Come see this one and make it yours!
